ent random projections are presented\nto demonstrate the viability and accuracy of the proposed approach.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Mar 2016 18:26:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Feb 2017 06:34:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 17 Apr 2017 15:52:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-18"}
