 still intuitively bother us.\nNonetheless, those conclusions should be no more challenging to our intuition\nthan Derek Parfit's thought experiments on the subject.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Mar 2016 19:17:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Aug 2016 17:56:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 4 May 2018 15:02:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-07"}
